<!--
  Verified FloSCRIPT: loads and solves Mobile_Demo-Steady_State example.

  Usage: Play via Flotherm GUI → Macro → Play FloSCRIPT → select this file.

  NOTE: This script uses project_unlock + project_load, which only works
